          "id": "c59fc2eb0057ef3016078d475bfffb11242be680",
          "message": "fix(vm/keeper): cherry-pick typeCheckCache stdlib fix from chain/gnoland1 (#5401)\n\n## Summary\n\nCherry-pick of #5400 (`fix(vm/keeper): make cold stdlib load populate\ntypeCheckCache`) from `chain/gnoland1` onto `master`.\n\n**Original PR**: #5400 by @thehowl\n**Original merge commit**: 96264d2\n\n## Goal\n\nKeep `master` in sync with the hotfix applied to `chain/gnoland1`. This\nPR validates that the fix also passes CI on `master` (which may differ\ndue to gas accounting changes).\n\n## Context\n\n`TypeCheckMemPackage` wasn't storing leaf stdlibs (22 packages like\n`time`, `regexp`, `math/rand`) in `vm.typeCheckCache`. This caused\nnon-deterministic gas consumption between fresh and restarted nodes,\ntriggering a consensus halt on gnoland1 at block 352922.\n\nSee #5400 for full details.\n\nCo-authored-by: Morgan <morgan@morganbaz.com>",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-01T11:08:07+02:00",
          "tree_id": "61339e371a00a6c782c00b0fd6a79d612414def6",
          "url": "https://github.com/gnolang/gno/commit/c59fc2eb0057ef3016078d475bfffb11242be680"
