          "distinct": true,
          "id": "df30676ac55c7824b9371ccb15248ce624099ce9",
          "message": "fix: add generic markdown customized banner (#5378)\n\n- Replace `GNOWEB_BANNER_TEXT` + `GNOWEB_BANNER_URL` with a single\n`GNOWEB_BANNER_TEXT` that accepts inline markdown\n- Banner content is parsed via goldmark, links get `target=\"_blank\"` via\nAST rewriting\n  - Input is single-line, capped at 400 chars\n\nExample: `GNOWEB_BANNER_TEXT='This is **beta** — [Learn\nmore](https://gno.land)'`\n\n<img width=\"1421\" height=\"183\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-03-27 at 11 52 13\"\nsrc=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f90c18e7-0d99-4c21-8257-68469125b8db\"\n/>\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Alexis Colin <alexis@jaunebleu.co>",
